| Date | Change |
|------|--------|
| 2026-05-27 | Merged from `FORLORN_RITUALANT_ENCOUNTER.md` into appendix. Silence Pressure + Thread Tension confirmed as canonical mechanical model. Toll Count system retained as alternate reference. |
